      • MODE_MENSTRUATION

        public static final int MODE_MENSTRUATION
        Mode of menstrual period. The bracelet calculates the menstrual period according to the set of setMenstruationDuration(int) setMenstruationCycle(int) setMenstruationLatest(Date). And according to setMenstruationAdvance(int) to decide in advance to remind menstrual period is coming.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • MODE_PREGNANCY_PREPARE

        public static final int MODE_PREGNANCY_PREPARE
        Mode of pregnancy prepare. Basically the same as MODE_MENSTRUATION, except that the probability of pregnancy will be calculated additionally
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • MODE_PREGNANCY

        public static final int MODE_PREGNANCY
        Mode of pregnancy. The bracelet calculates the due date according to the set of setMenstruationCycle(int) setMenstruationLatest(Date). And according to setPregnancyRemindType(int) to display different reminding interfaces.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • setMenstruationEndDay

        public void setMenstruationEndDay(int v)
        Set menstruation end day.

        Menstruation end day is the number of days between menstrual end time and start time. For example, if the getMenstruationLatest() is 2020-5-1 and the end time of menstruation is 2020-5-2, the parameter should set 1. This parameter only affects the first cycle of menstruation.

        Parameters:
        v - Limit[1-28]
